                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8986" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0584</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1389 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">他石攻玉：宁巢公司绩效管理的变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Other Mountain&#39;s Stone Can Polish Jade：The Path to Transformation of Performance Management in Ningchao Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">潘丽丽，苗雷，潘君</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州宁巢公寓运营管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绩效管理；激励机制；国企改革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Performance management; Incentive mechanism; reform of state-owned enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">COVID-19影响下诸多企业遭受前所未有的经营压力，而宁巢公司的方总却凭借其在民营企业中积累的丰富管理经验帮助公司实现从低活力到高绩效的蝶变。本案例回顾了方总如何识别并解构国企在绩效管理上的种种困境，并通过“两化专业”改革传统的师徒经验传授模式，以及“两表一报”制度和激励方案的修订，有效地将民营企业管理的灵活高效特点融入国企之中，逐步赋能公司的绩效管理。展现了借鉴民企管理的灵活性，通过精细化管理和人性化激励，激发国企员工潜力，引领宁巢公司在复杂多变的市场环境中稳健前行的历程。本案例旨在加强学员对绩效管理核心知识的掌握，引导学生深入思考民营企业绩效管理方法在国有企业的应用要点。案例也可为其他行业管理人员提供参考和借鉴，助力其绩效管理实践。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the influence of COVID-19, many enterprises have suffered unprecedented business pressure, but Mr. Fang of Ning Chao Company has helped the company to realize the leap from low vitality to high performance by virtue of his rich management experience accumulated in private enterprises. This case reviews how Mr. Fang identified and deconstructed the dilemmas of performance management in SOEs, and through the reform of the traditional teacher-apprentice experience transfer mode through the &quot;two professions&quot;, as well as the revision of the &quot;two forms and one report&quot; system and incentive programs, he effectively integrated the flexible and efficient features of private enterprises into SOEs. The company has effectively integrated the flexible and efficient features of private enterprises into state-owned enterprises and gradually empowered the performance management of the company. The case shows the process of drawing on the flexibility of private enterprise management, stimulating the potential of SOE employees through refined management and humanized incentives, and leading Ning Chao to move forward steadily in the complex and changing market environment. This case is designed to strengthen the students&#39; mastery of the core knowledge of performance management and guide them to think deeply about the application of private enterprise performance management ideas in state-owned enterprises. The case can also provide reference for other industry managers to help their performance management practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《绩效管理》、《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绩效管理概念及原则与流程；绩效目标的设计和分解；绩效激励方法的应用</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
